text: Victor Patrașco (born 26 September 1998) is a Moldovan football player who plays as a left-back for FC Shinnik Yaroslavl. He also holds Russian citizenship as Viktor Viktorovich Patrashko (). ==Club career== He made his debut in the Russian Premier League for FC Ufa on 15 April 2017 in a game against FC Amkar Perm.
